@startuml
title Flow F-001: Authentication

actor Client
participant "Authentication Endpoint" as AuthEndpoint
participant "Authentication Service" as AuthService
participant "Password Policy" as PasswordPolicy

Client -> AuthEndpoint: Submit credentials
AuthEndpoint -> AuthService: Authenticate request
AuthService -> PasswordPolicy: Verify secure policy
PasswordPolicy --> AuthService: Credentials valid
AuthService --> AuthEndpoint: Issue access token (bounded lifetime)
AuthEndpoint --> Client: Return token
@enduml
